      method: GET
      docs: ''
      source:

        query-parameters:

          dir: optional<GetDestinationsRequestDir>
          limit:
            type: optional<integer>
            validation:
              min: 0

          next:
            type: optional<string>
            validation:
              maxLength: 255
          prev:

            validation:
              maxLength: 255

                next: next
